author: herald.ie
title: IFTA Television Awards 2015 nominations: TV3 soap Red Rock leads with 7 noms
text:
The nominations for the IFTA Television Awards 2015 have been released and new TV3 soap Red Rock leads with seven nominations. David Hennessy (Adam Weafer) and Katie Kiely (India Mullen) in Red Rock 02 October 2015 09:38 AM
Chris O'Dowd's comedy series Moone Boy, meanwhile, has bagged five nominations. The Awards take place on October 22 at the DoubleTree Hilton in Ballsbridge, Dublin.
